headline: New leadership appointments at Keter Group to support North American growth strategy
summary: ANDERSON, Ind., September 09, 2025--Keter Group, the world’s largest resin-based consumer goods company, today announces two senior leadership appointments, underscoring its strategic focus on North America and its commitment to maintaining its position as a leading global industrial organization.
